'''Lidium''' was a rare, metallic [[Ore/Legends|ore]] that was mined on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. [[Mesa 291]] was a lidium [[Mining/Legends|mining]] operation on Bothawui. After an accident two generations before the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the mine was abandoned as [[Plasma/Legends|plasma]] fires raged through much of the five-hundred level structure.<ref name="Breakout" />

